<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        /* Reset CSS */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Geist Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #000000;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }

        /* ASAPA Colors */
        :root {
            --blue-primary: #1d4ed8;
            --blue-dark: #1e40af;
            --blue-light: #dbeafe;
            --black: #000000;
            --gray-dark: #4b5563;
            --gray-medium: #9ca3af;
            --gray-light: #f3f4f6;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: var(--blue-primary);
            color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* Content */
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        /* Typography */
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--blue-primary);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--blue-primary);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--black);
        }

        .small {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--gray-dark);
        }

        /* Button */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: var(--blue-primary);
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: var(--blue-dark);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: var(--gray-light);
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: var(--blue-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
            .container {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://asapa.org.br/logo.png" alt="ASAPA Logo">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <%- body %>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="https://facebook.com/asapa">Facebook</a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/asapa">Instagram</a>
            <a href="https://asapa.org.br">Website</a>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ASAPA - Associação de Surf das Areias do Campeche. Todos os direitos
            reservados.</p>
        <p class="small">Este e-mail foi enviado para <%= email %>. Se você não deseja mais receber nossos e-mails, <a
                    href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">clique aqui para cancelar sua inscrição</a>.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
